    "description": "In the first-person single-player game USS Tempest: Spaceship Simulator you take a journey through the stars and experience the ultimate mission of leading the fate of the spaceship and the crew. Set course to known space and gather the necessary resources to keep the ship running. Along the way, you will explore different events and planets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831540/extras/1dfab09eefdf9dadad616a9344554919.poster.avif?t=1771770040\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831540/extras/1dfab09eefdf9dadad616a9344554919.webm?t=1771770040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831540/extras/1dfab09eefdf9dadad616a9344554919.mp4?t=1771770040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experience first-person shooter action and puzzles in the story missions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831540/extras/8ac1949d1c7f3af13c02b93f8fb5de18.poster.avif?t=1771770040\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831540/extras/8ac1949d1c7f3af13c02b93f8fb5de18.webm?t=1771770040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831540/extras/8ac1949d1c7f3af13c02b93f8fb5de18.mp4?t=1771770040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Encounter different randomized situations onboard the ship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831540/extras/107bfd1a1e3d2da2fbbb8e9345401068.poster.avif?t=1771770040\" 