ything necessary to make your life easier!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Fight your way back home</strong> - Peacefully or with violence<br></li><li> <strong>Survive</strong>- Trade, maintain the ship and upgrade the systems<br></li><li> <strong>Explore</strong> - Events, Unknown Space and the USS Tempest</li></ul>",
